Depends on

OpenGL
QuickCheck
bytestring
binary
MonadRandom
SDL
SDL-ttf
network  (install network-2.3)
mtl

Compile with

ghc --make SnakeServer.hs -O2
ghc --make SnakeClient.hs -O2

Run with

./SnakeServer port
./SnakeClient addr port name

example:

./SnakeServer 4000
./SnakeClient localhost 4000 valdemar
